&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Salaried GP 4 - 8 sessions (maternity cover) &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Practice&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;We are a large two site, forward thinking and friendly practice located on the Wales/English border.  There are excellent transport links to North Wales, Chester and the Wirral.  We currently have 8 Partners and 5 part-time Salaried GP’s with a list size of in excess of 15,400 patients.  We are fully supported by a Clinical Pharmacist, an ANP, 7 Practice Nurses and 2 Health Care Assistants.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt; &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;We are a training practice for GP registrars and medical students and have had a good retention of registrars joining the team becoming salaried GP’s and partners.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt; &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;We currently use EMIS Web and hold the vasectomy contract for North Wales.  Our nurses lead on the Family Planning clinics fitting both coils and implants.  The practice has a well-organised and supportive administrative team.  &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt; &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Under normal circumstances there are regular team building and social get togethers.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt; &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Salaried GP Post&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;4-8 sessions to cover maternity leave until end December 2021&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Competitive salary and terms according to experience&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Start date as soon as possible&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt; &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;For an informal visit or further details, please contact Caron Davidson, Practice Manager on 01244 538797 or Ann Morgan Assistant Practice Manager on 01244 549592&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Email:  &lt;/em&gt;&lt;em&gt;Caron.davidson@wales.nhs.uk&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt; &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
